WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.466 --> 00:00:04.833
I’m still a step too late.

2
00:00:05.166 --> 00:00:07.633
In my previous life, Zhou Wanyun and I were both labeled as cruel.

3
00:00:07.733 --> 00:00:09.866
That same night, she drowned in the lake.

4
00:00:10.166 --> 00:00:11.966
Why are you here?

5
00:00:12.900 --> 00:00:14.100
After lunch,

6
00:00:14.266 --> 00:00:16.600
Sister Zhou said she wanted to take a walk by the lake.

7
00:00:16.933 --> 00:00:19.300
But after the west side, she never returned.

8
00:00:19.300 --> 00:00:23.266
So I came to look for her.

9
00:00:23.566 --> 00:00:25.833
This Lin Guiren is deliberately hiding something.

10
00:00:26.366 --> 00:00:27.866
In my previous life, Consort Yan

11
00:00:28.333 --> 00:00:30.700
didn’t cause any stir over Zhou Wanyun’s death.

12
00:00:31.400 --> 00:00:32.300
Chief Steward Li.

13
00:00:32.600 --> 00:00:35.900
Take Lin Guiren to the Ministry of Justice and put her under strict supervision by the Yan family.

14
00:00:36.100 --> 00:00:39.066
Quickly, find me five more.

15
00:00:43.366 --> 00:00:45.133
What did the Huang family do wrong?

16
00:00:45.133 --> 00:00:47.766
To be imprisoned and sentenced to death?

17
00:00:47.766 --> 00:00:49.000
This path

18
00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:51.633
is the only way to the imperial kitchen.

19
00:00:53.200 --> 00:00:55.866
Yuan, go to the imperial kitchen.

20
00:00:56.366 --> 00:00:58.366
Let me see what they’re doing.

21
00:01:02.133 --> 00:01:04.833
Consort, this medicine is rare.

22
00:01:05.100 --> 00:01:07.300
This month, only one dose has been produced.

23
00:01:07.300 --> 00:01:09.200
Use it at a suitable time.

24
00:01:09.666 --> 00:01:10.966
Understood.

25
00:01:11.666 --> 00:01:13.766
But why do I feel

26
00:01:14.066 --> 00:01:16.300
the Emperor seems more energetic after drinking it?

27
00:01:16.533 --> 00:01:18.400
Are you sure the medicine is fine?

28
00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:21.233
The Consort personally asked for it from Shen Yipei, so it should be fine.

29
00:01:21.366 --> 00:01:23.900
It must be the dosage is too little.

30
00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:26.600
Tell him to increase the dosage.

31
00:01:30.666 --> 00:01:33.900
Consort, when the servant went to get the medicine, Zhou Caixian discovered it.

32
00:01:34.133 --> 00:01:35.266
To avoid leaks,

33
00:01:35.266 --> 00:01:36.966
the servant had to drown her in the lake.

34
00:01:36.966 --> 00:01:38.700
It was made to look like an accidental drowning.

35
00:01:38.766 --> 00:01:40.366
A cruel person is just that.

36
00:01:40.366 --> 00:01:41.533
Dead is dead.

37
00:01:41.533 --> 00:01:44.633
What’s the panic? Get up.

38
00:01:45.966 --> 00:01:48.000
Consort, it’s not good.

39
00:01:49.133 --> 00:01:51.400
The Emperor has handed over the governing seal to Consort Rong.

40
00:01:51.666 --> 00:01:52.566
What?
